---
---
<section id="contacto" class="border-t border-neutral-100">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr]">

    <div class="px-5 md:px-8 py-14 md:py-20 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-neutral-100">
      <span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-400">Contacto</span>
    </div>

    <div class="px-7 md:px-16 py-14 md:py-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">

      <div>
        <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xs mb-10">
          ¿Necesitás visualizar tu proyecto? Contanos de qué se trata y te respondemos a la brevedad.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-[11px] text-neutral-400 font-light">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-300 block mb-1">Email</span>
            contacto@estudio.com.ar
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-300 block mb-1">Teléfono</span>
            +54 11 0000-0000
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-300 block mb-1">Dirección</span>
            Av. Corrientes 1234, Piso 8<br />Buenos Aires, Argentina
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/XXXXXXXX" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
        <div>
          <label class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-400 block mb-2">Nombre</label>
          <input
            type="text" name="name" required
            placeholder="Tu nombre"
            class="w-full border-b border-neutral-200 text-xs text-neutral-900 py-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-neutral-900 transition-colors bg-transparent placeholder-neutral-300"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-400 block mb-2">Email</label>
          <input
            type="email" name="email" required
            placeholder="tu@email.com"
            class="w-full border-b border-neutral-200 text-xs text-neutral-900 py-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-neutral-900 transition-colors bg-transparent placeholder-neutral-300"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-400 block mb-2">Mensaje</label>
          <textarea
            name="message" required rows="4"
            placeholder="Contanos sobre tu proyecto..."
            class="w-full border-b border-neutral-200 text-xs text-neutral-900 py-2.5 focus:outline-none focus:border-neutral-900 transition-colors bg-transparent placeholder-neutral-300 resize-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-neutral-900 border border-neutral-900 px-6 py-3 hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 mt-2"
        >
          Enviar
        </button>
      </form>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
